summary: You have until midnight tonight to join the Secret Santa! Here how to join if you want to:
title: You have until midnight tonight to join the Secret Santa! Here how to join if you want to:
body:
To sign-up send an email to sansansecretsanta@yahoo.com( I will not be accepting sign-ups via Ask, because I need a more reliable way than Tumblr to contact you) with these 3 things:

  1. Your Tumblr Username/URL
  2. A 5(maximum) word prompt for your Santa
  3. Are you willing(but not guaranteed) to create & receive smut? Yes Smut or No Smut

Once you have sent your email I will get back to you twice. The first time will be to let you know I have received your email. If I do not get back to you within 24 Hours of you sending your email message me and I’ll get back to you as soon as possible. The second time you will hear from me is when the Sign-ups are over and I send you the name of your giftee with their prompt.

By signing up to the SanSan Secret Santa you are agreeing to these big things:

  1. DO NOT REVEAL YOUR IDENTITY. That should go without saying that you need to keep your identity a secret until the big reveal.
  2. Your gift could be anything as long as it is free, digital, and rebloggable on Tumblr. Your gift could be anything from fanfiction, fan videos, gif sets, handcrafted creations, and anything else you can think of! The only thing is the gift needs to be COMPLETE & ORIGINAL. And minimum length for fanfics is 1,000 words.
  3. TAGGING IS ESSENTIAL. The first two tags need to be #SanSan Secret Santa and #[Recipiant Name].
  4. We require that you leave your Ask open for Anons and that you send your partner AT LEAST 1 lovely, Anonymous Secret Santa message/week.  You must also reply to at least one message per week so we can confirm your blog is active.
  5. Don’t change your URL before December 22. Your Santa needs to be able to find you, so keep the same name until the big day.

If you have any other questions or comments just send me an ask here and I’ll get back to you as soon as possible.

summary: It slips out by accident. They're not even talking, just sitting in the same room while Sansa fusses over some letters and...
body:
It slips out by accident. They’re not even talking, just sitting in the same room while Sansa fusses over some letters and Theon…watches her, he supposes. The fact that she wants him around and even more, that she wants him around just for his own sake will never make sense, but he certainly won’t complain.

Still, he watches her brow furrow slightly and he doesn’t catch himself before the, “Everything alright, love?” slips out.

She looks up and his eyes widen, prepared to take it back. Her mouth settles into a startled ‘O’ and…she blushes? He can’t quite tell in the light.

After a long moment, she manages to say, n as dignified a tone as she can muster, “I am fine, my…Theon. Thank you.”

He nods and turns away, shocked enough thst he said anything. In his haste to turn away, he doesn’t notice her looking back at him the same way.

summary: Though snow had blanketed the heights of the Giant’s Lance above, below the mountain the autumn lingered and winter wheat was...
text: Though snow had blanketed the heights of the Giant’s Lance above, below the mountain the autumn lingered and winter wheat was ripening in the fields. Outside the window she could hear the laughter of the washerwomen at the well, the din of steel on steel from the ward where the knights were at their drills. Good sounds.
source: The Winds of Winter, Alayne I
